sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh Container
    participant Puller as model-serving-puller<br/>8084/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(Triton/OVMS/MLServer/TorchServe)
    participant Client as External Client

    rect rgb(200, 220, 255)
        Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Loading (Puller + Adapter Mode)
        MM->>Puller: LoadModel(modelId, modelPath)<br/>gRPC / localhost / no auth
        Puller->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS / TLS 1.2+ / Provider credentials
        Storage-->>Puller: Model files
        Note over Puller: Write artifacts to<br/>/models/{modelId}/
        Puller->>Adapter: LoadModel(modelId, localPath)<br/>gRPC / localhost / no auth
        Note over Adapter: Adapt model layout<br/>to runtime format
        alt Triton
            Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelLoad(modelName)<br/>gRPC / 8001 / localhost
        else OVMS
            Adapter->>Runtime: POST /v1/config/reload<br/>HTTP / 8001 / localhost
        else MLServer
            Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelLoad(modelName)<br/>gRPC / 8001 / localhost
        else TorchServe
            Adapter->>Runtime: RegisterModel(marUrl)<br/>gRPC / 7071 / localhost
        end
        Runtime-->>Adapter: Load confirmation
        Adapter-->>Puller: LoadModel response (size, maxConcurrency)
        Puller-->>MM: LoadModel response
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Loading (Embedded Puller Mode)
        MM->>Adapter: LoadModel(modelId, modelPath)<br/>gRPC / localhost / no auth
        Adapter->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS / TLS 1.2+ / Provider credentials
        Storage-->>Adapter: Model files
        Note over Adapter: Download + adapt layout<br/>in single step
        Adapter->>Runtime: Load model (runtime-specific)<br/>localhost / no auth
        Runtime-->>Adapter: Load confirmation
        Adapter-->>MM: LoadModel response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 220, 220)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3: Inference Request (Passthrough - bypasses adapter)
        Client->>MM: Inference request<br/>gRPC / varies / varies
        MM->>Runtime: Forward to runtime (direct)<br/>gRPC / localhost / no auth
        Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
        MM-->>Client: Inference response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 200)
        Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 4: Model Unloading
        MM->>Puller: UnloadModel(modelId)<br/>gRPC / localhost / no auth
        Puller->>Adapter: UnloadModel(modelId)<br/>gRPC / localhost / no auth
        alt Triton
            Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelUnload(modelName)<br/>gRPC / 8001
        else OVMS
            Adapter->>Runtime: POST /v1/config/reload (remove from config)<br/>HTTP / 8001
        else MLServer
            Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelUnload(modelName)<br/>gRPC / 8001
        else TorchServe
            Adapter->>Runtime: UnregisterModel(modelName)<br/>gRPC / 7071
        end
        Runtime-->>Adapter: Unload confirmation
        Note over Puller: Delete model files from<br/>/models/{modelId}/
        Adapter-->>Puller: UnloadModel response
        Puller-->>MM: UnloadModel response
    end
